**Title:** Delete a habit <br>
**Description:** **As a** user **I want** to delete existing habits  
**So that** I can keep my habits up to date  

**Acceptance Criteria:**  
- A “Delete” option is available for each habit  
- Confirmation prompt is shown before deleting a habit  
- Deleted habits are permanently removed from the list and database  
- Remaining habits are displayed correctly after deletion  

**Priority:** High  
**Story Points:** 4  
